Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.85,0:00:13.52,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}The brilliant glow of this sky, does it carry right into your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.83,0:00:22.91,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,1600)\3c&H141414&}The melody you heard in your dream, it plays like the silence
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.53,0:00:28.12,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Even if your hands are still far from that dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.12,0:00:33.34,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Come now and remember that kindly voice
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.34,0:00:46.28,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(50,200)\3c&H141414&}Someone was there singing for you, the happiness they sang about
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.28,0:00:55.68,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Sound of the sky, echo on high, break through that overwhelming sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.68,0:01:00.62,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Everything that shines in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.62,0:01:06.08,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,400)\3c&H141414&}Is part of the real world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.34,0:01:15.55,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,200)\3c&H141414&}Even your tears can't leave you here to stay forever
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.71,0:01:27.51,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,4000)\3c&H141414&}In this gentle light pouring down onto you, play tomorrow's song
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:19.47,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&00&}The Visitor - A Snowy Field Ablaze
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.38,0:22:46.45,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - put these feelings together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.45,0:22:49.24,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}And sing of how important they are
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.59,0:23:07.72,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I was so happy that I cried
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.56,0:23:13.69,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}It hurt so bad that I laughed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.52,0:23:22.53,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}But that all just goes to show that I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.53,0:23:26.66,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,800)}Let's just walk it slowly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.66,0:23:28.35,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}Everybody singing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.35,0:23:32.64,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Just tell me a bit of what you think
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.64,0:23:33.96,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}You're just my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.96,0:23:39.97,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - even though they might waver
Dialogue: 1,0:23:37.00,0:23:39.97,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&\an8}I know, you know, little happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.97,0:23:45.80,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I want us to echo on forever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.71,0:23:45.80,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&\an8}Can you hear my precious note?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.80,0:23:52.18,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}All these words that there are can't even describe it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.18,0:23:57.93,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1400)}Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.93,0:24:02.57,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1400)}Can you hear it? Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.65,0:04:28.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Witch of Helvetia?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.02,0:08:21.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A Helvetian soldier?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:45.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I? Am I a hostage of the Helvetians?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.91,0:08:52.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So you have taken me as a hosta-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:19.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Infantry of the Roman Empire, First Tank Division. Thirteenth Tank Battalion, Company B, {\i1}Feldwebel{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:24.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A'ishah Aldora. Identification Number 1031021.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.28,0:09:31.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Infantry of the Roman Empire, {\i1}Feldwebel{\i0}, A'ishah Aldora.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.01,0:09:37.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Identification number 1031021.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.56,0:11:07.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so I actually made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.11,0:11:10.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandmother...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:56.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I need energy to escape, that's why I'm eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.94,0:12:18.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, have any of you seen the bones of the angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.41,0:12:27.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, you don't understand anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.09,0:13:30.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:35.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know that such trumpets still existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:39.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,May I try?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.28,0:14:07.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A great trumpet... That I'm able to see something like th-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:14:59.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.48,0:15:02.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.67,0:16:18.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Yumina.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:26.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I serve the Helvetian Orthodox Church.\NMay the blessings of all be upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.44,0:16:28.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're one of those heretics.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:33.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one god. Such a greeting is blasphemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.38,0:16:42.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.63,0:16:49.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't talk, it will cause a lot of trouble for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:56.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If you feel the least bit thankful, then you should talk honestly with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.89,0:17:09.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not allowed to talk about my mission,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.30,0:17:14.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,but I wanted to see the bones of the angel that are supposedly in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.51,0:17:30.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My grandmother, she was in this fortress, in this stronghold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.49,0:17:36.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She was taken prisoner on the Eastern front, where she met my grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.67,0:17:42.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was a child, she often told me about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.24,0:17:52.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I always wanted to see it, the angel my grandmother had seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.44,0:17:57.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Angel of the Apocalypse that had brought divine retribution upon the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.18,0:21:28.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Her name is Noël.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.39,0:21:32.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël? Noël Kannagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.35,0:21:33.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:37.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The one that unleashed the Invisible Death?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.99,0:01:44.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, this snow is so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.67,0:01:49.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And headquarters sending us on a patrol? On a day like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.26,0:01:50.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.42,0:01:55.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You still haven't given up on Madame Jacquotte?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.95,0:01:58.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that, I-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.07,0:02:06.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever. Just keep looking and looking and then you can say "maybe" when you just can't find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:10.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.64,0:02:15.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking that you were kind of like Rio for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.31,0:02:27.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.75,0:02:32.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Under the cliff, eleven o'clock. About 400 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:51.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up. Can you wake up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.38,0:02:57.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Her clothes are all frozen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.55,0:03:00.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata. Take her coat off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:02.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're switching.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.23,0:03:05.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.53,0:03:10.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A Roman soldier?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:36.57,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,To restore operations at a facility like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:40.93,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are the greatest genius in the history of the Academy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.93,0:03:43.82,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,We can win with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:47.58,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,We owe this to you, Miss Noël Kannagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:54.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.77,0:04:03.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They found her during their patrol. A Roman soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.35,0:04:07.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like her left leg is broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:14.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Her fingers are turning black!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:21.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Frostbite. If we don't work fast, she may lose those fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.43,0:04:34.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me take care of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:46.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like she'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.31,0:04:48.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she saved her fingers, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:49.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:51.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Noël?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:54.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she'll stay with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:56.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder why...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:58.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She put everything she had into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.92,0:05:02.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost like she was repairing the Takemicaduchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.15,0:05:04.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.97,0:05:11.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A bugle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:13.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She might be a scout.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:15.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:18.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.64,0:05:20.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:24.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No one would expect to see a Roman soldier in a place like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:29.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that. This is the first time I've seen a Roman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.21,0:05:37.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone calls them the enemy and everything, so I thought they would look more evil or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.33,0:05:41.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Romans might think the same way about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.84,0:05:50.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When I saw her, I thought that maybe the Romans were just like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:52.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, what are you-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:56.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, it's about time. The Recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.65,0:06:08.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The peace conferences still aren't going smoothly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.44,0:06:10.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:13.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we going to report this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:19.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If we do, she'll be taken to the capital and interrogated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.06,0:06:28.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do anything about that! She stepped into enemy territory at a time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.53,0:06:30.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A soldier must be prepared for torture-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.22,0:06:31.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Interrogation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.64,0:06:38.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I will decide how we handle her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:43.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me some time, Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.58,0:06:48.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.19,0:06:52.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We are soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.09,0:07:02.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.11,0:07:06.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When you carried her here, did anyone see you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,0:07:11.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. I was focused on bringing her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:14.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:37.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, Rio. What would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.52,0:08:32.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.66,0:08:49.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Roman. I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:57.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that scream?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.25,0:08:58.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:02.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:05.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:27.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:33.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What is your mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:42.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You have some nerve...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.67,0:09:46.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it? Find anything out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:50.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely nothing! She doesn't understand Helvetian at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:55.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,All we've figured out is her identification number and that her name is A'ishah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:10:01.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Lieutenant Filicia Heidemann. I am in command here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:08.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are some nice breasts you have. Just what I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.99,0:10:11.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind if I sucked and massaged them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.95,0:10:14.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind if I play with your body?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.54,0:10:21.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, Commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,0:10:25.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like she really doesn't understand Helvetian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:30.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a problem. It means we can't interrogate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.96,0:10:34.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to find someone who speaks Roman quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.79,0:10:36.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.77,0:10:43.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we can interrogate her and file a report, we will hold her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.44,0:10:44.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:48.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we might test our luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:52.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever happens, it's not my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.30,0:10:58.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A'ishah, welcome to the Time-Telling Fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.06,0:11:00.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Time-Telling Fortress?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.39,0:11:02.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. The Time-Telling Fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:17.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an3\pos(1840,1050)}Sound of the Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:22.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an1\pos(80,1050)}Sound of the Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:27.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.61,0:11:30.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Is it too hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.11,0:11:50.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She ate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.13,0:11:52.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.21,0:12:00.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She must be saying it's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.64,0:12:03.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.21,0:12:07.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata's always like that, but why is Noël acting like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.52,0:12:11.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Atonement, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.87,0:12:20.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Engel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:30.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have studied Roman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.65,0:12:33.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. If we could talk to her, maybe-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.75,0:12:39.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.73,0:12:44.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yumina. Got enough hands to shovel snow at the church?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:48.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The children are working very hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:49.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:53.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They sure are growing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:55.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:13:00.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,People grow every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.60,0:13:03.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the sound of Miss Kanata's trumpet...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:07.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio would say she still has a ways to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:11.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Didn't you head over to Treize to stock up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:15.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Things happen. Ended up being a wasted trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.16,0:13:18.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like things aren't going your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:24.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me. I've been hearing some ugly rumors about the fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.87,0:13:29.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:43.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Rio would let you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.22,0:14:08.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.62,0:14:12.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! This is absolutely wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.34,0:14:17.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Iliya's sound echoed in me, it echoed in Rio,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.67,0:14:23.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,and the same piece echoed in both Helvetia and Rome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:27.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound will echo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.13,0:14:31.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether in Rome or Helvetia, it's the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.00,0:14:46.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Temporary repairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:00.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Danke?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.39,0:15:04.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What does "Danke" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.77,0:15:06.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It means "Thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.60,0:15:12.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone saw us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.83,0:15:25.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This town never saw the lions mouth, but parents, siblings, and relatives included, everyone's lost someone they knew in the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.35,0:15:29.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the nicest people, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.41,0:15:35.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You remember the owner of the distillery, Mikhail?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:41.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I had some business with him yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:45.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the Helvetian army's on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.17,0:15:47.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,To this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:55.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If that has anything to do with this Roman soldier you've got here, then we've got a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:16:02.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, we have to ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:07.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Naomi, do you know anyone who knows Roman?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.46,0:16:10.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I know anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:35.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's she saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.31,0:16:37.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a light greeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:40.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need any of that! Ask her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.62,0:17:18.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She says she wants to see the bones of the angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.72,0:17:20.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Bones of the angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.49,0:17:21.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.06,0:17:33.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My grandmother was a soldier at the Time-Telling Fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.67,0:17:40.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She was captured on the Eastern front and met her grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.93,0:17:45.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was young, she often told me about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:18:00.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That is not what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.44,0:18:02.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A demon brought the world to ruin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.80,0:18:06.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't care. Just tell us what she's saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:12.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She wanted to see the Angel of the Apocalypse that brought divine retribution upon the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:15.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She says that's why she came.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.69,0:18:19.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A call to march?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.86,0:18:21.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This code is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.44,0:18:28.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,First Royal Guard Battalion, Ninth Independent Mobile Division.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.89,0:18:32.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ninth? Isn't that Colonel Hopkins'?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:35.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he famous?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:38.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They call him the Demon of Binnenland.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:44.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They say he revived ancient weapons and wiped out three whole towns in a single night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:52.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. He doesn't know you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.50,0:18:54.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.01,0:18:58.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless, you don't have much time to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.09,0:19:02.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You girls need to figure out what to do, and fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:03.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to hand her over, or-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.32,0:19:05.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing to think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.25,0:19:08.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We are Helvetian soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:11.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like I lost this bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:14.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't make it in time, Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:15.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.76,0:19:20.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio said she didn't want anyone else to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.44,0:19:23.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she would do everything she could!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:25.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she went!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.61,0:19:30.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.98,0:19:32.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.52,0:19:34.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all a part of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:40.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The following is an order from the Commander of Platoon 1121.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.50,0:19:49.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This order is my own decision. I will take full responsibility for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.91,0:19:51.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you all understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.16,0:20:06.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Platoon 1121 Commander, Lieutenant Filicia Heidemann.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.18,0:20:10.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Several days ago, a Roman scout was captured in Treize.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:16.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, due to an accident during interrogation, we were unable to confirm several details.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.86,0:20:22.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Immediately following, we heard reports of Roman forces in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.92,0:20:24.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know anything about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.87,0:20:27.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not, Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:29.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.50,0:20:37.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,As of this moment, command of Fortress 1121 has been transferred to the Ninth Independent Mobile Division.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:49.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't start shouting now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.03,0:20:50.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:55.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A'ishah just told me about the legend of the Maidens of the Fire, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:58.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's different. According to her-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:01.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I want a complete search!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:03.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Found her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.99,0:21:04.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How about over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.95,0:21:05.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not here either!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.78,0:21:07.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Find her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.18,0:21:08.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Open this door!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.44,0:21:11.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She must be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:12.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Put a guard at every gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:25.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She says that she still doesn't know your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.42,0:21:26.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:40.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Invisible Death?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.53,0:21:51.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? A rat, I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.72,0:21:53.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Noël!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.01,0:22:10.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.29,0:22:12.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Fortress 1121.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.70,0:22:20.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A large contingent of Roman forces has appeared on the border between Seize and Nomansland?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.13,0:24:14.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(960,405)\c&H020202&\bord0}Next time: Echo Through the Blue Sky
